The paper deals with covert communication in wireless networks, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the security aspect of wireless networks, which falls under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of relay networks is a common technique in multimedia communication (cs.MM) and the paper discusses the impact of increasing the relay's maximum transmit power, which is a system-level optimization (cs.SY).
